attributeSource.infoString2: REMAX Town & Country - Blue Ridge Downtown

data.description:
LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!!!
3BR/2Bath mobile home on 11.11 acres just outside of town.  This land has been in my family for 48+ years but my children are grown and we want to downsize. This property is located 0.8 miles from BLUE RIDGE, Georgia, the home of the beautiful scenic railway. The new EMS/911 center is also located at the end of Windy Ridge Road. The land is in a prime location for development opportunities.  The real estate is surrounded by paved road with untouched timber covering all but the home area. My property is in Fannin County but connnected to the city limits of Blue Ridge. We have well water, but city water and sewage are available due to our proximity. University of North Georgia College is being constructed approximately 1 mile away. Would make a great investment opportunity of possible student housing or duplexes.
data.whatILove: Proximity to town but still not in town. Location. Quiet and solitude.
